a database, right?

00:05:54.940 --> 00:05:58.660
So a single database or a single
network cannot be the network

00:05:58.660 --> 00:05:59.800
of networks.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:02.500
And so that was the big flaw,
and that's what led to, I

00:06:02.500 --> 00:06:06.580
think, Stefan having this
ah-ha moment of the need

00:06:06.580 --> 00:06:09.610
for something like ILP, which
was a dangerous moment for--

00:06:09.610 --> 00:06:12.193
STEFAN THOMAS: It was scary at
