should put all your balances

00:06:17.020 --> 00:06:17.650
on this ledger.

00:06:17.650 --> 00:06:19.108
You should do all
your transactions

00:06:19.108 --> 00:06:21.040
through this one system.

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:22.630
And we knew the
friction from that,

00:06:22.630 --> 00:06:25.300
but then again, stepping back
from that and suddenly saying,

00:06:25.300 --> 00:06:27.210
oh, there are going
