around, what's

00:06:36.900 --> 00:06:39.460
XRP's role in this new
world, and how do we

00:06:39.460 --> 00:06:41.890
make sure that our
technologies are

00:06:41.890 --> 00:06:45.970
still needed and still necessary
and can benefit this new world?

00:06:45.970 --> 00:06:47.470
How do we re-architect
everything

00:06:47.470 --> 00:06:49.370
to serve this new world?

00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:51.760
So I think we're still in
the process of rolling out

00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:53.510
all of the different pieces.

00:06:53.510 --> 00:06:55.810
But it was that 1 year
period from, I would,

00:06:55.810 --> 00:07:01.180
say mid-2014 when we first
had that realization,

00:07:01.180 --> 00:07:04.090
to October 2015 when the white
paper for Interledger came

00:07:04.090 --> 00:07:04.630
