00:07:36.820 --> 00:07:37.600
CHRIS LARSEN: And
if you look at--

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:39.970
stepping way back, the
macro problem that we think,

00:07:39.970 --> 00:07:43.300
again, the world has is lack
